{
  "stem": "20083.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 21.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But we heard the screams of the mice and the rats during the night when they were-- they were-- when they were dying.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] something that I remember-- yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In Warth Mill in this particular factory, there was one section for some reason, they had-- before we actually were sent to Warth Mill, they had just captured a German U-boat crew.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this U-boat crew-- before they actually transported them to a prisoner of war camp-- was also stationed at-- in Warth Mill.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had their own corner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when we arrived, we noticed that somebody had painted a long, chalk, colored square.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were not supposed to cross this square because this was the domain of the Nazi U-boat crew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when they heard that we were all Jewish refugees, they said, Judenschweine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But they couldn't do anything to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were just standing there screaming at us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They said, soon-- I mean, in German of course-- soon Hitler will be here, and then it will be like this for you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we screamed back, the Nazi swine, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then one--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody was guarding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing is that some British soldiers were stationed outside this Warth Mill factory so that none of us could escape.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what happens inside was of no concern of theirs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I can tell you the right of way, nothing ever happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no battle, no fight but-- except for the insults that we screamed at each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But one night-- we were not supposed to go to the bathroom at night because the bathroom was outside the actual building.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
